name: Holo Cyngn Template
body: # Holo-Cyngn BETA So this is a theme of CaynogenMod , i think I think it works well with the other rom with the T-Mobile Theme. I think it's a cool theme maybe not very personalized (I hate those who then go to modifcare everything and then maybe you can see qaulcosa bad), but what I customized it's done right! FOR NOW (maybe if I feel like it is put in charge, do not you want to pluck so it will be a low figure in the average of the other issues we are: P), the theme is free but all rights are reserved! If you want to use as a template for your theme. ![screen 1](https://lh4.ggpht.com/xPJJw5GjjptK4JGqahS28ymev1vLPaHqqBPDc8UJNNBW47wu3_71xoRBsPcUvMsn9w=h310-rw) ![SCREEN2](https://lh6.ggpht.com/QgJGqy45Px6LEa-9hht4vDfwwROIkinMyE4jZwJnstpVu1erPmdKoBSYjCzLZuy0aU5Z=h310-rw) ![screen 3](https://lh4.ggpht.com/GtY25e-sr-BhZ-dq4ihxsmkpHZ_ufnzQb4btyHguhPUYYy-9mlSXG67Ud1k9J_4-65ci=h310-rw) ``` $ git clone https://github.com/BottyIvan/Holo-Cyngn-Template $ cd BottyIvan/Holo-Cyngn-Template ``` That being said I hope you like it!
